flowchart TD
    A[User accesses login] --> B[Enter username/password]
    B --> C{Validate credentials}
    C -->|Invalid| D[Show error message]
    D --> B
    C -->|Valid| E[Hash password & verify]
    E --> F{Authentication successful?}
    F -->|No| D
    F -->|Yes| G[Generate JWT token]
    G --> H[Return token to client]
    H --> I[User authenticated]
    I --> J[Access protected routes]
    J --> K[End]

    style A fill:#e1f5fe
    style K fill:#c8e6c9
    style D fill:#ffcdd2